Terminal commans in Angular
To create new app

ng new app1
to add a new component to an existing application
cd app1
ng generate component greet

To add a class to an existing application
ng generate class product
to add a new service to an existing application
ng generate service productservice

to generate new pipe 
ng generate pipe mypipename


to run application
npm start
  or
ng serve --open








Pipes in Angular
Pipes formats the content in the tewmplates.

Two types
1. Pure pipes
2. Impure pipes

1. Pure pipes
----------------
All pure pipes in angular are builtin pipes
ex:
1. Lowercase
2. Uppercase
3. Datepipe
4. Currencypipe
5. Jsonpipe
6. Percentage pipe
7. Decimal pipe
8. Slice pipe


2. Impure pipes
-----------------
Any kind of pipe which triggers all the time by using keyboard, mouse events

Ex:
All custom pipes created by the programmer
